-Grbic,M (2296) Belgrade 2013 1/2-1/2 (54)}) 9. Bd2 {Black has a cramped
position} Ne7 10. O-O-O {White has a king attack} Ke8 $2 (10... Bd6 $14) 11. g3
$4 {weakening the position} (11. Nb5 $142 {would have given White the upper
hand} Bd6 12. Bb4 $18) 11... Bg4 $11 {Black threatens to win material: Bg4xd1}
12. Rde1 Nc6 13. h3 {White threatens to win material: h3xg4} Bf3 14. Rhg1 Nd4 (
