) 36... axb5 37. cxb5+ (37. c5 $5 Bd7 $18) 37... Kxb5 $16 38. Kc3 Kb6 39. Bd5 (
39. Bc4 Ba4 40. Kd3 Bd1 $16) 39... Bb5 (39... Ba4 $142 $5 $11 {and Black has
air to breath}) 40. Bc4 $16 Ba4 41. Bd3 (41. Kd2 $142 $16) 41... Bd1 $11 {
Black threatens to win material: Bd1xf3} 42. Kc4 $2 (42. Kd2 $142 {and White
can hope to live} Bxf3 43. Ke3 $11) 42... Bxf3 $19 43. Kd5 $4 {terrible, but
the game is lost in any case} (43. Bf1 $142 Bxe4 44. Kc3 $19) 43... Bg2 44. Ke6
