) 9... Bd7 10. Ngf3 O-O-O (10... e5 11. O-O e4 12. Bb5 $11) 11. Qe2 Nf6 12.
O-O-O Kb8 13. Rhe1 Rhe8 14. Nc4 Nd5 15. g3 {Secures f4} Ka8 16. Nce5 Nxe5 17.
