19. Nxa8 Bc3 $11) 17... Nxc3 (17... Nxf4 $142 {and the scales tip in favour of
Black} 18. gxf4 Qh4 $19) 18. Rxc3 $15 Bxc3 19. Qxc3 {Black wins the exchange}
Qd5 (19... Re8 $142 20. Rd1 Qe7 $15) 20. Kg2 $4 {hands over the advantage to
the opponent} (20. Bh6 $142 {is the best option White has} f6 21. Bxf8 Rxf8 22.
