28. Qc3 (28. Qf4 Re8 $15) 28... Rxa2 $15 29. Rf4 Qd5+ (29... Re8 $5 30. Qf3 Qd5
31. Qxd5 cxd5 32. Rg4+ Kh8 $17) 30. Kh3 $11 {White has a mate threat} Qh5+ $4 {
gives the opponent new chances} (30... h5 $142 {was possible} 31. Qe3 Qe6+ 32.
