{[%mdl 8192] A03: Bird's Opening with 1...d5} 1. f4 d5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. e3 Nc6 4.
Bb5 Bd7 5. Bxc6 $146 (5. O-O e6 6. b3 Bd6 7. Bb2 O-O 8. d3 a6 9. Bxc6 Bxc6 10.
Nbd2 Qe7 11. Qe1 Ba3 12. Bd4 Nd7 13. Qg3 f6 14. Rae1 Bb4 15. Ba1 e5 16. Nh4 Qe6
17. Re2 Rae8 18. f5 Qd6 19. Qg4 Rf7 {Rodriguez Vila,A (2559)-Mekhitarian,K 
(2416) Santos 2007 1/2-1/2 (39)}) 5... Bxc6 {Black has the pair of bishops} 6.
O-O e6 7. b3 {Covers a4} b6 8. Bb2 Be7 9. Qe1 Bb5 10. d3 {Controls c4+e4} Qd6
11. a4 {White threatens to win material: a4xb5} Ba6 12. Nbd2 h6 {Prevents
intrusion on g5} 13. Ne5 Nh5 (13... O-O 14. Rf3 $14) 14. b4 (14. Ndf3 c5 $16)
14... c5 {Black threatens to win material: c5xb4} (14... Qxb4 15. Ba3 Qc3 16.
Bxe7 Kxe7 17. Qh4+ Nf6 18. Ndf3 $11) 15. Qd1 {White threatens to win material:
Qd1xh5} Nf6 16. bxc5 bxc5 17. Ba3 Nd7 {Black threatens to win material: Nd7xe5}
18. Ndf3 Qc7 (18... O-O 19. Qe1 $11) 19. Nxd7 Qxd7 20. Ne5 Qc7 21. Qg4 {
White threatens to win material: Qg4xg7} Bf6 22. Rfe1 h5 {Black threatens to
win material: h5xg4} 23. Qf3 Rc8 24. e4 Bb7 (24... d4 25. Nc4 $11) 25. exd5
Bxd5 26. Qe2 g6 (26... h4 27. Rab1 $11) 27. c4 {White threatens to win
material: c4xd5} Bb7 28. Rab1 Be7 $4 {solves nothing} (28... Bc6 29. Bxc5 Bxg2
30. Kxg2 Qxc5 31. Rb7 $14) 29. Qb2 $4 {there were better ways to keep up the
pressure} (29. Nxf7 $142 {and White takes home the point} O-O 30. f5 $18) 29...
Ba8 $16 30. Qb5+ (30. Nc6 O-O 31. Nxe7+ Qxe7 $16) 30... Kf8 $14 {Black loses
the right to castle} 31. Bc1 (31. Bb2 $5 {should be considered} Kg8 32. Nxg6
fxg6 33. Bxh8 Kxh8 34. Rxe6 $11) 31... Kg7 $11 32. Bd2 (32. Bb2 f6 33. Qa6 Bd6
34. Nxg6 Kxg6 35. Rxe6 Bc6 36. Rxf6+ Kh7 $17) 32... Rb8 (32... f6 33. Nf3 Qd6
34. Qb2 $17) 33. Qd7 (33. Qa6 $5 $11 {has some apparent merit}) 33... Qxd7 $17
34. Nxd7 Rxb1 35. Rxb1 Bc6 {Black threatens to win material: Bc6xd7. Black
forks: a4+d7} (35... Rd8 $5 36. Ne5 f6 $15) 36. Ne5 $11 {White threatens to
win material: Ne5xc6} Bxa4 (36... Ba8 $142 $5 $11 {would keep Black in the game
}) 37. Ra1 $16 Bc2 38. Rxa7 Kf6 $4 {strolling merrily down the path to disaster
} (38... Re8 $142 $16) 39. Bc3 $18 Re8 40. Nc6+ Kf5 41. Nxe7+ Kxf4 42. Bd2+ Ke5
43. Nc6+ Kf6 44. Bc3+ Kg5 (44... e5 {is one last hope} 45. Rc7 Bxd3 46. Nxe5
Bb1 $18) 45. Rxf7 Bxd3 (45... Kh6 {a fruitless try to alter the course of the
game} 46. Bg7+ Kh7 47. Bf6+ Kg8 48. Rg7+ Kf8 49. Ne5 Rb8 50. Rh7 Rb1+ 51. Kf2
Rf1+ 52. Kxf1 Bxd3+ 53. Kg1 Kg8 54. Rh8#) 46. Bd2+ Kh4 47. Rf4+ Kg5 48. Rf3+
Kh4 49. Rxd3 (49. Rg3 Bxc4 50. Bg5#) 49... e5 (49... Kg4 {cannot change what
is in store for ?} 50. Rf3 h4 51. Ne5+ Kh5 52. g4+ hxg3 53. Rxg3 Kh4 54. Kg2
Rh8 55. Rh3#) 50. Rd5 (50. Rg3 e4 51. Bg5#) 50... g5 51. Nxe5 Rxe5 52. Rxe5 Kg4
53. h3+ Kg3 54. Rf5 (54. Rf5 g4 55. Be1#) (54. Bxg5 h4 55. Re3#) 1-0

